# Service and Store Patterns

- Services are Axios API wrappers only; no UI logic or React hooks.
- Stores manage client state and call services, not raw API endpoints.
- Type all API responses with generics.
- Keep auth tokens in `expo-secure-store`, never in plain storage.
- Handle 401 by clearing auth state and redirecting to login flow.
